Subject: [Haleon] General and Device Control Dashboards display "Oops an Error Occurred" message
Description:
When attempting to access either the General dashboard (Dashboard > General Dashboard) or Device Control dashboard (Device Control > Dashboard), Haleon's production environment displays the "Oops an Error Occurred" message. 

(Creating support ticket for better tracking)
Solution_Comment__c: Issue has been resolved by backend specific files on the backend. After rerunning cron job, dashboards are appearing again
